{"tid":307784,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[合法]查卷大法","createTime":"2017-07-03T15:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T05:47:15.000Z","uid":107233,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb652434aa65648af7468a97e106cb3a5ac689a","tid":307784,"uid":107233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"出完grade之後，大家發現死得不明不白又可以點？appeal? 咪傻啦。好多科啲卷都唔會派返，有時都唔知死喺邊。試過 send email 俾professor 諗住睇卷，不過只有大約一半會覆，而且唔一定會俾你睇marksheet，敷衍下你就算。其實同學係可以根據私隱條例入紙申請 assessment 資料來睇，而校方係唔可以拒絕，試過幾次係work嘅。<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n<br />\n- 下載表格 <a href=\"https://www.pcpd.org.hk/english/publications/files/Dforme.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcpd.org.hk%2Fenglish%2Fpublications%2Ffiles%2FDforme.pdf&d=2yJKmZabdA9LydBmBOmedQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9b1e7cba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcpd.org.hk/english/publications/files/Dforme.pdf</a><br />\n- 填妥表格：Data user 就係學校名(e.g. HKU), Data subject 就係你本人<br />\n- Part 4 係重點，要小心填寫，視乎你想囉到咩資料，舉例:<br />\n<br />\nFor ENGGxxxx, ARTSxxxx, SOSCxxxx, and CAESxxxx, I request the mark sheets and examiners' comments given for the final exam.<br />\n4. 之後 email 或 hard copy 交去自己 faculty office<br />\n5. Faculty office 會確認收到，而且要係40日內交到俾你，收費$5/頁<br />\n<br />\n咁當然哩個係一個轉折嘅方法，亦會增加admin staff 既工作量，同時要俾錢。但係我認為俾同學知道呢啲資料係應份嘅。當然，科科A+就唔洗煩啦！<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：HKU Code of Practice of Personal Data Protection <a href=\"https://uis.hku.hk/web/gsabc/pdpo_cop.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuis.hku.hk%2Fweb%2Fgsabc%2Fpdpo_cop.pdf&d=2yJKmZabdA9LydBmBOmedQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=21b87d47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://uis.hku.hk/web/gsabc/pdpo_cop.pdf</a> (need portal login); HKU Privacy Policy Statement <a href=\"http://www.hku.hk/about/policies_reports/privacy_policy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hku.hk%2Fabout%2Fpolicies_reports%2Fprivacy_policy.html&d=2yJKmZabdA9LydBmBOmedQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=17286215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hku.hk/about/policies_reports/privacy_policy.html</a><br />\n法理上其他U一樣"},{"pid":"084254539b336c3563cbb040bdfcb600ba620194","tid":307784,"uid":7519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"ust小毒毒留名<br />\n平時send email 比ta都唔敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28f55e0885787fcaa92eedeb0d984cd7b3cbd11d","tid":307784,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"法例上有冇話要keep 幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好憎department, grad 左都想拎返幾年前d 卷黎睇下，增加班粉皮既workload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316c483d3b4d8f864a93829476d2ed02f2a70084","tid":307784,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:43:44.000Z","msg":"好黑箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3003078a0c694166fb27057f7635a6dee24bc623","tid":307784,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"你玩到咁串 小心present project 個grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003b2bdfdb6ecafa3daef45040e542b5b52f7758","tid":307784,"uid":107233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法例上有冇話要keep 幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好憎department, grad 左都想拎返幾年前d 卷黎睇下，增加班粉皮既workload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHKU內部指引60日"},{"pid":"a9247a29a02f849d168ab13ca6ba3ffce4fc92f1","tid":307784,"uid":107233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:50:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你玩到咁串 小心present project 個grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱啱1st hon grad <img src=\"/asset